    "body": "This is because we don't store checkpoint state for epoch with skipped slot in the current implementation, it's implemented here https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/blob/v0.30.0/packages/lodestar/src/chain/blocks/stateTransition.ts#L79\r\n\r\nWhenever we pass checkpoint, we should store it in the checkpoint state cache because that checkpoint state may become justified/finalized state later and we need it.\r\n\r\n@dapplion could you confirm this?",
